desc: Dukhni develops fine Arabic Perfumery products with Oud, Bakhoor Incense & Traditional Attar Oils! We are taking top notch Arabic Aromatics to the world! Inspired by a vision to blend luxury and natural with a set of 100 year old recipes of Bakhoor Incense, passed down five generations of our family

layout.text: Transport yourself to Arabia with a Dukhni Ma’amoul Bakhoor Variety Box & Exotic Burner
5 Ma’amoul Bakhoor Scents & a low smoke, exotic burner!
